Copyright © 2019 Forum of Incident Response and Security Teams, Inc. (FIRST).
Licensed under Creative Commons CC-BY-SA (Attribution-ShareAlike).
ZettelForge implements the IEP 2.0 Framework as governance nodes in its
knowledge graph. The IEP 2.0 JSON Specification is available at
https://www.first.org/iep. Per CC-BY-SA, any derived IEP specification
schemas distributed by this Software are shared under the same license.
This share-alike obligation applies only to the IEP-derived schema
