### 6.3 Scope of Third-Party Obligations

The CC-BY-SA obligation on FIRST IEP 2.0 applies exclusively to the IEP
policy schema definitions (the JSON schema structures implementing IEP 2.0
fields) distributed within this Software. It does not extend to, and does not
create any open-source obligation for, the remainder of the Software,
including but not limited to the memory engine, knowledge graph implementation,
entity indexing, alias resolution, synthesis layer, API layer, governance
framework, or any other proprietary component.

